Lusca[1] is the NPM module for use with Express that comes in the KrakenJS middleware (open sourced by PayPal).<p><pre><code>    app.use(lusca.csrf());
    app.use(lusca.csp({ /* ... */}));
    app.use(lusca.xframe(&#x27;SAMEORIGIN&#x27;));
    app.use(lusca.p3p(&#x27;ABCDEF&#x27;));
    app.use(lusca.hsts({ maxAge: 31536000 }));
    app.use(lusca.xssProtection(true));
</code></pre>
[1] <a href="https://github.com/krakenjs/lusca" rel="nofollow">https://github.com/krakenjs/lusca</a>
